    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-3">Budget Option: $5 to $15 per Hour</h3>
    <p class="text-slate-400 mb-4 leading-relaxed">Certified teachers on See Guru and community tutors on iTalki offer lessons at these rates. See Guru ensures consistent quality through credential verification, while on iTalki you should read reviews carefully. Look for tutors with specific business experience mentioned in their profiles.</p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-3">Mid-Range Option: $15 to $30 per Hour</h3>
    <p class="text-slate-400 mb-4 leading-relaxed">Professional tutors with verified credentials and business backgrounds typically charge in this range. You get more consistency and targeted expertise at this price point.</p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-3">Premium Option: $30 to $60 per Hour</h3>
    <p class="text-slate-400 mb-4 leading-relaxed">Top-rated tutors with corporate training experience, advanced certifications, or native-level business writing skills charge here. Worth it if you have urgent career goals or need executive-level communication coaching.</p>

